Sentence: Two complexes of mTOR have been identified: complex 1, consisting of mTOR - Raptor ( regulatory associated protein of mTOR) - mLST8 ( termed mTORC1), and complex 2, comprising mTOR - Rictor ( rapamycininsensitive companion of mTOR) - mLST8 - Sin1 ( termed mTORC2).
